# 📜 LICENSE — brain-ai

## Open Protocol License

*(MIT-Compatible)*

---

## Preamble — Statement of Intent

brain-ai was created to explore a fundamental question:

> *What remains of communication when infrastructure disappears?*

This project exists as a **protocol**, not a product.
As an **idea**, not a service.
As an **experiment in resilience**, not control.

The intent of brain-ai is to enable communication:

* without central authorities
* without fixed infrastructure
* without semantic assumptions in transit
* without exclusion by geography, power, or technology

This license exists to **guarantee freedom of use**, while preserving the **ethical neutrality** and **open survival** of the protocol.

Authorship is acknowledged.
Control is not imposed.

— *josemarpoubel*

